snippet.title: GingerSnap -  Gameplay Clip 2  - Dash Mechanics!
snippet.description:
Trying something new. Being a Sonic fan, I love speed mechanics in games. But I'm not sure if I've seen a game do something like this before so I thought I would take a second to explain it.

Anyone remember those old Smash Bros Dojo updates? Those were so cool. I doubt people would care as much about some dinky little indie game but hey it's worth a try!

Thank you for taking the time to read this description, you're cool!
